      <h1>Hotels</h1>

      <p class="mb-6">
        The conference will take place at Cleveland State University Student Center in downtown Cleveland.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Official PyOhio Hotel</h2>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <p class="mb-2">
          <strong
            ><a
              href="https://www.ihg.com/crowneplaza/hotels/us/en/cleveland/cleps/hoteldetail"
              class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Crowne Plaza Cleveland at Playhouse Square</a
            ></strong
          > ⭐⭐⭐ - 0.4 miles
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Located in the theater district with easy access to the venue. This is the official PyOhio hotel for 2025. If
          you want a hotel within close walking distance and the likelihood of running into other attendees in the
          lobby, book here.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6 italic text-gray-600">
          We have a limited hotel block available for a short time. Book early to secure your room at the conference
          rate.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <a
            href="https://www.crowneplaza.com/redirect?path=asearch&brandCode=CP&localeCode=en&regionCode=1&hotelCode=CLEPS&checkInDate=24&checkInMonthYear=062025&checkOutDate=28&checkOutMonthYear=062025&rateCode=6CBARC&_PMID=99801505&GPC=PYO&cn=no&viewfullsite=true"
            class="button has-icon color-primary text-xl"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <Icon name="mdi:bed" />
            Book Room with PyOhio Block
          </a>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            The block defaults to 07/24/2025 → 07/28/2025. Be sure to select the specific dates of your stay.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

